{"tid":2424681,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有冇人睇過天航嘅D系列？","createTime":"2021-02-26T18:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T18:57:21.000Z","uid":211994,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa9029ac9bc6c976f780674258f022031e5f654","tid":2424681,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T18:36:58.000Z","msg":"終於出到最後一本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有生之年系列<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQaya5C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQaya5C.png&h=bd14938f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多謝佢為咗俾多啲小朋友有書睇特登賣平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但原來佢近呢幾年都過得唔太如意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n妻子過世，要父兼母職一定唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢妻子本散文集賣得並唔係太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v8CXCMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv8CXCMi.png&h=7780c075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，因為書展取消咗，D系列嘅新書發佈都受影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家Patreon有連載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實體書遲啲會出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uwVutTb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuwVutTb.png&h=9f898831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天航嘅Patreon<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3s60LsR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3s60LsR&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=5c67a41e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3s60LsR</a><br />\n<br />\n天航嘅FB:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/152506018099285/posts/4453252544691256/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F152506018099285%2Fposts%2F4453252544691256%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B3